    answer: "Yes, if built correctly. I use encrypted form delivery, BAAs with form providers when needed, and don't store PHI in any non-compliant system. I'll walk you through the options so you pick what fits your compliance posture.",
  },
  {
    question: 'Do you handle ongoing updates?',
    answer: "30 days of post-launch support is included. After that, small updates are \$50–\$150 each, or I can set you up on a \$100–\$200/mo retainer if you need regular changes. Most practices self-manage after launch.",
  },
  {
    question: 'How do you rank me for "dentist near me" in Lynchburg?',
